getWord(String) - Method in class app.function.Function
Used to read a all the characters before a operation Exemple: - getWord("x+2") = "x"; - getWord("sin(x+ln(x))+x") = "sin(x+ln(x))"; - getWord("(ln(x)*sin(x))") = "(ln(x)*sin(x))"; The word can be : a numeric number, a operation , a base function (x,y,z) , or a complex function(sin,cos ...)
